ed!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dep1665702806421.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dep1665702806421.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dep1665702806421.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dep1665702806421\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Bind To\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines how Uniface finds the COM object class—by <code class=\"ph codeph\">ProgId</code> or\n         <code class=\"ph codeph\">CLSID.</code></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dep1665702806421__section_w2091ab1b5b1_w2092ab1b5_w2093ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dep1665702806421__table_d13004e1_d13005e1_d13006e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dep1665702806421__table_d13004e1_d13005e1_d13006e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dep1665702806421__table_d13004e1_d13005e1_d13006e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dep1665702806421__table_d13004e1_d13005e1_d13006e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">ProgID</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dep1665702806421__table_d13004e1_d13005e1_d13006e1__entry__2\">Binding to a ProgID is more flexible than\n                        binding to a CLSID, but the interfaces supported by the name may\n                        change.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dep1665702806421__table_d13004e1_d13005e1_d13006e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">CLSID</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dep1665702806421__table_d13004e1_d13005e1_d13006e1__entry__2\">Binding to a CLSID is absolute, but\n                        compatibility with new releases of third-party software may cause\n                        problems.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dep1665702806421__section_tzq_gdz_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d742003e111\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dep1665702806421__ul_uxw_3dz_cxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dep1665702806421__li_d42728e1_d42729e1_d42730e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qnm1665702714020.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qnm1665702714020.html\" title=\"A Signature Implementation is a Development Object that defines the technology used to implement a signature, such as Uniface, COM, SOAP and so on. A Signature can have multiple implementations. Each Signature Implementation captures the technology-specific properties of the Signature, Signature Operation, and Signature Parameters.\">Signature Implementation</a> (COM) </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612546\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612546\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Bind To Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Bind To Determines how Uniface finds the COM object class—by ProgId or CLSID. Value Description ProgID Binding to a ProgID is more flexible than binding to a CLSID, but the interfaces supported by the name may change. CLSID Binding to a CLSID is absolute, but compatibility with new releases of third-party software may cause problems. Applies To Signature Implementation (COM) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}